    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like a \"block.\" a block implies it's coming back. this feels more like... a finality. like the core of me is just gone. i feel like i'm just a ghost inhabiting a body that used to have a purpose. if the thing that made me *me* is dead, then what's the point of the shell? it feels so hollow.",
